(define/contract (count-servers n logs x queries)
  (-> exact-integer? (listof (listof exact-integer?)) exact-integer? (listof exact-integer?) (listof exact-integer?))
  (map (lambda (query)
         (let ((active-servers (make-hash)))
           (for ([log logs])
             (let ((id (car log))
                   (time (cadr log)))
               (when (and (<= (- query x) time) (<= time query))
                 (hash-set! active-servers id #t))))
           (- n (hash-count active-servers))))
       queries))
